articles.author: AJIT SOLANKI, SIBI ARASU and MUNIR AHMED
articles.title: India, Pakistan brace for winds, flash flooding as Cyclone Biparjoy heads for evening landfall
articles.description: MANDVI, India (AP) — A vast swath of western India and neighboring southern Pakistan that suffered deadly floods last year are bracing for a new deluge as fast-approaching Cyclone Biparjoy whirls toward landfall Thursday.
